06152022 Bash Redirection and Output

https://www.nhooo.com/note/qa5cxa.html

/dev/stderr
/dev/stdin
/dev/stdout
/dev/null

file descriptor
0 stdin
1 stdout
2 stderr
n file

echo 'hello' > /dev/null 2>&1
echo 'hello' 'goodbye' > /dev/null 2>&1

exec 3> /tmp/filedescriptorthree
echo "This is a test" >&3
date >&3
cat /tmp/filedescriptorthree
exec 3<&-
echo "File /tmp/filedescriptorthree closed"